Description:
NOT JUST YOUR AVERAGE JO!
"While the Average Joe's dodgeball team was hit and miss, this property is a clear winner."
Join us at Joanne Way this week to view an extraordinary property. No joke, this would be one of the neatest properties I've ever seen - has the carpet in the bedrooms even been walked on?
Just around the corner from Officer Secondary School and over the road from public transport, 33 Joanne Way is less than two years old and packed with features:
- Four bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Two separate living zones;
- Kitchen with all the modern appliances;
- Double car garage with rear and internal access;
- Stunning backyard with alfresco and decking overlooking the manicured landscaping.
Don't be the Johnny-come-lately as this property is sure to sell.
